OL,3,CThousands still living in 'unsafe'
OL,4,Cbuildings in Wales seven years after
OL,5,CGrenfell
OL,7,FSeven years after 72 people died in
OL,8,Fthe Grenfell Tower disaster, thousands
OL,9,Fof people across Wales are still
OL,10,Fliving in buildings with serious fire
OL,11,Fsafety issues.
OL,13,FThe issue of building safety was
OL,14,Fbrought to the forefront of public
OL,15,Fconsciousness in 2017 when a deadly
OL,16,Ffire rapidly spread through the London
OL,17,Ftower block, accelerated by cladding
OL,18,Fwhich was not fire-retardant, trapping
OL,19,Fthe helpless residents in their
OL,20,Fapartments.
