OL,3,CThousands still living in 'unsafe'
OL,4,Cbuildings in Wales seven years after
OL,5,CGrenfell
OL,7,FIn the aftermath of the disaster, fire
OL,8,Fsafety defects were found in buildings
OL,9,Facross the UK, including hundreds in
OL,10,FWales.
OL,12,FLast year the signed a pact with
OL,13,Fdevelopers to carry out remediation
OL,14,Fwork at 345 buildings where issues had
OL,15,Fbeen identified. But 12 months later,
OL,16,Fwork is yet to commence on more than
OL,17,Fhalf the affected buildings.
