OL,7,FCampaigner Mark Thomas, who is part of
OL,8,Fthe Welsh 'Cladiators' group, told ITV
OL,9,FWales's Sharp End programme: "At the
OL,10,Fend of the day we hold developers
OL,11,Fresponsible, not the but because
OL,12,Fdevelopers have been so poor in their
OL,13,Fresponse you naturally look to the
OL,14,Fgovernment for support.
OL,16,F"And one of the key things the
OL,17,Fgovernment can do is legislate and put
OL,18,Fin a legal framework that then people
OL,19,Fcan go to.
