OL,3,CThousands still living in 'unsafe'
OL,4,Cbuildings in Wales seven years after
OL,5,CGrenfell
OL,7,FUntil buildings are remediated,
OL,8,Fresidents usually face sky high costs
OL,9,Ffor things like insurance and waking
OL,10,Fwatches. It's also impossible to sell
OL,11,Faffected properties without making a
OL,12,Fsignificant loss, meaning they are
OL,13,Feffectively trapped in their unsafe
OL,14,Fapartments until work is carried out.
OL,16,FRuth Wainwright and Eileen Fletcher
OL,17,Fboth bought their apartments in for a
OL,18,Fquiet retirement with their husbands.
OL,20,FSadly, both men died without seeing
OL,21,Fthe issues resolved.
