OL,7,FShe said: "This has been a very long
OL,8,Fsaga indeed and it's had some of the
OL,9,Fmost complicated things that we've had
OL,10,Fto navigate that I've ever seen in all
OL,11,Fthe time I've been doing this kind of
OL,12,Fwork."
