OL,7,FThe Developers Pact was signed a year
OL,8,Fago by 11 major property developers
OL,9,Fand committed to the principle that
OL,10,Fleaseholders should not have to foot
OL,11,Fthe bill for remediation work. It also
OL,12,Fsaw developers agree to carry out the
OL,13,Fnecessary work as soon as possible but
OL,14,Fthere was no specific timeframe set
OL,15,Fout within the contract.
