OL,7,FThe House Builders Federation, which
OL,8,Frepresents British property
OL,9,Fdevelopers, said in statement: "The
OL,10,Findustry is absolutely committed to
OL,11,Fremediating all buildings in line with
OL,12,FGovernment requirements and removing
OL,13,Fany financial burden from leaseholders.
OL,15,F"Significant progress is being made
OL,16,Fbut agreeing the scope of works and
OL,17,Fgetting contracts in place with
OL,18,Fbuilding owners, leaseholders, and
OL,19,Fother relevant parties unavoidably
OL,20,Ftakes time.
